author: Hal Boedeker
title: Tracy Morgan visits Magic Kingdom
text:
Caption Tracy Morgan at the Magic Kingdom Chloe Rice/Disney 
Actor-comedian Tracy Morgan, fiancée Megan Wollover and daughter Maven Morgan, 2, take flight Thursday on Dumbo the Flying Elephant at Magic Kingdom theme park. The family celebrated Maven Morgan’s 2nd birthday at Walt Disney World Resort in Lake Buena Vista. 
Actor-comedian Tracy Morgan, fiancée Megan Wollover and daughter Maven Morgan, 2, take flight Thursday on Dumbo the Flying Elephant at Magic Kingdom theme park. The family celebrated Maven Morgan’s 2nd birthday at Walt Disney World Resort in Lake Buena Vista. (Chloe Rice/Disney) Caption Actor Alan Cumming at Walt Disney World Chloe Rice / Walt Disney Co. Tony Award-winning actor Alan Cumming poses with Mickey Mouse and Minnie Mouse at Magic Kingdom on April 13, 2015. Cumming turned 50 years old this year, celebrated his birthday with friends and family at Walt Disney World. (Note his Mickey-inspired shirt with his birth year on it too.) Cumming won his Tony for "Cabaret" in 1998, and is currently seen on CBS's "The Good Wife," for which he has won an Emmy.
